# https://arayinfosolutions.com/
# This is the ros2 carla9.14 integration.
# Related files can be found under our aray-ai github repository.
# https://github.com/aray-ai/carla-0.9.14

Please read this before installing the carla ros

1. System requirements
	-Ubuntu 20.04 as OS
	-Docker installed
	-nvidia GPU
2. Software used-
	- carla version 9.14
	- ROS2 Humble
	- Python 3.10 environment

3. All the Docker files are stored in the respective folders.
4. They are ready to use.

5. Below are the important docker commands..

6. To compile the docker images- 
   docker build --tag <image_name> .
   
7. If you make and change in the Dockerfile and want to rebuild the image- 
   docker compose build --no-cache <service_name>
   
8. If you all the images are ready, to compose the container for final run- 
   docker compose up --build

9. If you are using the prebuild images from the image folder, you first need to mount those images-
   docker load -i carla9.14_python3.10.tar


